---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | SendTheBid"
  description="SendTheBid privacy policy. We don't collect personal data, use cookies, or require accounts. Your calculations stay in your browser."
  currentPath="/privacy"
>
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p class="text-text-primary font-medium">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
        <p>SendTheBid is a free tools site for tradespeople. We don't collect your personal data, we don't use cookies, and we don't require accounts. Everything runs in your browser.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">What We Don't Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>No personal information (name, email, phone)</li>
          <li>No cookies or tracking pixels</li>
          <li>No account registration</li>
          <li>No calculator inputs or results</li>
          <li>No financial data from invoices or estimates</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Your Data Stays Local</h2>
        <p>All calculations, invoices, estimates, and other documents are generated entirely in your browser. Nothing is sent to our servers. When you generate a PDF, it's created client-side using your browser's print function.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Cloudflare Analytics, which is a privacy-first analytics service. It does not use cookies, does not track individual users, and does not collect personal data. It only provides aggregate page view counts so we know which tools are useful.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Hosting</h2>
        <p>SendTheBid is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect standard server logs (IP addresses, request timestamps) as part of their infrastructure. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We load Google Fonts (Barlow Condensed and Inter) for typography. Google may collect anonymized usage data through font requests. No other third-party services are used.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Changes</h2>
        <p>If we ever change this policy, we'll update this page. Since we don't have your email, we can't notify you directly — but the "Last updated" date at the top will reflect any changes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Reach us at <a href="mailto:privacy@sendthebid.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@sendthebid.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
